  <refsect1>
	<title>History</title>
	<para>
	  The <package>liburi</package> library implements an alternative API to
	  that provided by the
	  <package><ulink url="http://uriparser.sourceforge.net/">uriparser</ulink></package> library, which <package>liburi</package> uses internally.
	</para>
  </refsect1>
  
